Tournament: <%= @tournament.name %>
Event: <%= @event %>

<% if @event == "match_scored" %>
A tournament match result has been recorded.

Match ID: <%= @payload[:match_id] %>
Winner Team ID: <%= @payload[:winner_id] %>
<% elsif @event == "registration_status_changed" %>
A tournament registration status has changed.

Registration ID: <%= @payload[:registration_id] %>
Player ID: <%= @payload[:player_id] %>
New Status: <%= @payload[:status] %>
<% else %>
A tournament event has occurred.
<% end %>

Timestamp: <%= Time.current.iso8601 %>
